Arreglemos el UI
=====
class: small-code

```{r, echo=TRUE, eval=FALSE}
library(shiny)

shinyUI(fluidPage(
  
  titlePanel("Old Faithful Geyser Data"),
  
  sidebarLayout(
    sidebarPanel(
       sliderInput("bins",
                   "Number of bins:",
                   min = 1,
                   max = 50,
                   value = 30)
    ),
    mainPanel(
       plotOutput("distPlot")
    )
  )
))

```

arreglemos la UI
==========
class: small-code

```{r, eval=FALSE}
library(shiny)

shinyUI(fluidPage(
  
